e/person/details/G3P9-RYZ Hanzlik - Vojtech (1876-)] [with wife Frantiska to meet a cousin Rosicky. He previously lived in Polanka]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:JX8Y-B27|title=New York Passenger Arrival Lists (Ellis Island), 1892-1924|last=Hanzlik|first=|date=1900|website=FamilySearch|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n|\n|c. 1901\n[[Ellis Island|New York]]\n|[https://www.familysearch.org/tree/person/details/G3PS-3DX Hanzlik - Frantisek (1874-)]\n|\n|-\n|\n|c. 1901\n[[Baltimore]]\n|[https://www.familysearch.org/tree/person/details/L14N-B66 Houdek - Matej (1877-1947),] [https://www.familysearch.org/tree/person/details/L14N-YYC Marie (1884-1962)]\n|\n|-\n|\n|c. 1902\n|[https://www.familysearch.org/tree/person/details/L1KG-9MF Skala - Josef (1885-1958)]\n|\n|-\n|17 April 1902\nSS Hannover\n[[Bremen]][[File:SS_Hannover.jpg|center|thumb]]\n|2 May 1902\n[[Baltimore]]\n|[https://www.familysearch.org/tree/person/details/L1K4-DX8 Hurtak - Jan (1876-1973)]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:2CSX-JJ5|title=Maryland, Baltimore Passenger Lists, 1820-1948|last=Hurtak|first=|date=1902|website=FamilySearch|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=}}</ref>\n\n[https://www.familysearch.org/tree/person/details/L1KX-7BD Kotesovec - Anna (1877-1952)]\n\nAnna was the younger sister of Marie and Vaclav and the older sister of Josef.\n|[[File:Anna Kot\u011b\u0161ovcov\u00e1-Vesecky (1877-1952).png|center|thumb|171x171px|Anna Kot\u011b\u0161ovcov\u00e1-Vesecky (1877-1952)]]\n|-\n|27 September 1902\n[[SS Main (1900)|SS Main]]\n\nBremen[[File:S.S. Main.jpg|center|thumb|168x168px]]<br />\n|11 October 1902 (2:36 PM)\n[[Ellis Island|New York]]\n|[https://www.familysearch.org/tree/person/details/G3P9-PW6 Hanzlik - Josef (1872-)] [with wife Marie and a married woman Helena Moutvic. He previously lived in Polanka]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://familysearch.org/ark:/61903/1:1:JF25-M4F|title=New York